## 🔌 API Contract

### Auth
```
POST   /api/auth/login         → { email, password } → { token, user }
POST   /api/auth/logout        → (header: Bearer token)
```

### Laporan
```
GET    /api/laporan            → list semua laporan (filter & pagination)
GET    /api/laporan/{id}       → detail laporan
POST   /api/laporan            → buat laporan baru (upload foto + koordinat)
PUT    /api/laporan/{id}       → update status (admin only)
DELETE /api/laporan/{id}       → hapus laporan (admin only)
```

### Dashboard
```
GET    /api/dashboard/stats    → { total, per_status, per_keparahan }
GET    /api/dashboard/peta     → list koordinat untuk map markers
```

### Python FastAPI (Internal — tidak expose ke publik)
```
POST   localhost:8000/detect
Request:  { image_base64: "data:image/jpeg;base64,..." }
Response: {
  success: true,
  jumlah_lubang: 3,
  keparahan: "parah",
  confidence: 0.87,
  foto_hasil_base64: "...",
  deteksi: [{ label: "pothole", confidence: 0.92, bbox: [x,y,w,h] }]
}
```

### Standard JSON Response CI4
```json
// Success
{ "status": true, "message": "Berhasil", "data": { ... } }

// Error
{ "status": false, "message": "Pesan error", "errors": { ... } }
```

