## ⚙️ Konfigurasi Server VPS

### Nginx — Frontend (Next.js port 3000)
```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name yourdomain.com;
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:3000;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;
    }
}
```

### Nginx — Backend (CI4)
```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name api.yourdomain.com;
    root /var/www/backend/public;
    index index.php;
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$query_string;
    }
    location ~ \.php$ {
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php/php8.1-fpm.sock;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $realpath_root$fastcgi_script_name;
        include fastcgi_params;
    }
}
```

### Supervisor — FastAPI (background process)
```ini
[program:pothole-fastapi]
command=/usr/bin/python3 -m uvicorn main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000
directory=/var/www/ai-service
autostart=true
autorestart=true
stderr_logfile=/var/log/fastapi.err.log
stdout_logfile=/var/log/fastapi.out.log
```

